    "800303": {
        "Desc": "Search for the Defiled Statue",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This is it, right? Okay then, use your Elemental Sight to look for the eye!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooooh... So what did you see?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? ...Nothing? But Paimon was so excited..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's going on...? Are you sure you did it right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "This requires another method."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "Using Elemental Sight on a Field Tiller is of no use because it is not powered by the elements."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "Let me give it a try."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "...And done."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wowwww! It's, it's the...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "The very thing the Abyss Herald has been seeking all along â€” the eye of the first Field Tiller."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "All of the Ruin Guards today are just replicas of this machine. As the prototype, its combat capability was unrestricted."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Prototype\"? ...Paimon doesn't know that word, is it another ancient term from Khaenri'ah?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "As the Abyss Order has surmised, if this eye is placed in the hands of the Defiled Statue..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "And if the limbs of Osial, Overlord of the Vortex, are attached to the statue... there you have a mechanized god."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "And this newly born god will have the power to \"topple the divine thrones of Celestia.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What an extreme and dangerous operation."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Abyss Order must be stopped."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "Yes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Thâ€”Then... What should we do with this eye?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Hide it somewhere no one will find it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Put it under the guardianship of the Church of Favonius."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "No. I'll guard it myself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!? You!? Dain... You won't go and do anything crazy with it, will you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "You may doubt me if you wish, but I must ensure it does not fall into the wrong hands."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "No matter where we may hide it, they will find it. And as for the Church of Favonius â€” well, you know I don't trust them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, hehe... right..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "But our work isn't done yet. To avoid any further repercussions, we must also take care of that Defiled Statue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "By doing what, exactly?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Can we let the Church take care of this one?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "We can't have the Church get involved. Let's handle it ourselves. As for what I mean by take care of it... naturally, I mean to completely destroy it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Dâ€”Destroy it!? That's a Statue of The Seven! As well as being a really important cultural relic, they're actually divine, too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh, well, good thing we didn't tell Barbara earlier. Otherwise, she'd be going completely bonkers right now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "Hmph... Do The Seven really expect me to help them look after what belongs to them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "Let's go back to <color=#00E1FFFF>those ruins</color> and destroy the inverted statue. If we are lucky, we will also run into that Abyss Herald."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dainsleif",
                    "T": "I'll make sure it doesn't get away this time."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
